rmation security office web site rates this service is available to faculty staff and departments by subscription and is charged monthly to your department's it services bill see the computing services rates web page getting started requests for server hardware installations cabling and removal of hardware must be submitted via the it services orderit portal for ordering assistance please call the service desk at 650 725 help option 2 for ordering last modified tue 6 sep 2011 at 11 02 pages about this service overview business documents for server hosting main campus actions orderit find answers submit a helpsu request stanford answers related pages server hosting auxiliary data center footer links stanford university helpsu user login stanford university terms of use copyright complaints
